%N A397702 Numbers k such that sigma(k) = psi(k) + tau(k)^5 + omega(k)^5.
%e A397702 1405957 is a term since sigma(1405957) = 1640000 = 1607200 + 8^5 + 2^5 = psi(1405957) + tau(1405957)^5 + omega(1405957)^5.
%o A397702 (PARI) isok(k) = {my(f = factor(k)); sigma(f) == prod(i=1, #f~, (f[i, 1]+1) * f[i, 1]^(f[i, 2]-1)) + numdiv(f)^5 + omega(f)^5; } \\ _Amiram Eldar_, Jul 05 2026
